      <title>中东紧张局势令交易员震惊，股市“紧张不安”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/stock-market-is-on-edge-as-middle-east-tensions-jolts-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在创下历史新高一天后，美国股市周二回落，有报道称伊朗正准备在未来 12 小时内向以色列发射弹道导弹袭击，导致波动性加剧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/stock-market-is-on-edge-as-middle-east-tensions-jolts-traders</guid>
