    <item>
      <title>罢工导致美国东部和墨西哥湾港口关闭，威胁经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-dockworkers-strike-set-to-go-ahead-after-no-deal-announced-m1pwyo3k</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在总统大选前几周，美国东部和墨西哥湾沿岸的所有主要港口的码头工人举行了近 50 年来的首次罢工，此次罢工可能波及全球最大经济体，并在造成政治动荡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/us-dockworkers-strike-set-to-go-ahead-after-no-deal-announced-m1pwyo3k</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 04:03:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗向以色列发射火箭弹 油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗向以色列发射火箭弹后，油价飙升，这可能加大该地区原油供应中断的可能性，该地区原油产量占全球原油总产量的三分之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-1</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 23:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：伊朗袭击报道推动债券上涨、油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[有报道称伊朗在黎巴嫩发动“有针对性的地面袭击”后袭击了以色列，投资者撤退到更安全的市场角落，导致债券和黄金价格上涨，而股票下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 30 Sep 2024 22:49:29 GMT</pubDate>
